<style data-mw-deduplicate="TemplateStyles:r1033289096">.mw-parser-output .hatnote{font-style:italic}.mw-parser-output div.hatnote{padding-left:1.6em;margin-bottom:0.5em}.mw-parser-output .hatnote i{font-style:normal}.mw-parser-output .hatnote+link+.hatnote{margin-top:-0.5em}</style><div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">For other people with the same name, see <a href="/wiki/Lakatos_(disambiguation)" class="mw-redirect" title="Lakatos (disambiguation)">Lakatos (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<p class="mw-empty-elt">
