<li><a href="/wiki/Lakatos_Award" title="Lakatos Award">Lakatos Award</a> set up in memory of him</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Alexander_Tarasov-Rodionov" title="Alexander Tarasov-Rodionov">Alexander Tarasov-Rodionov</a>, author of "Shokolad" which was formative of Lakatos' early political thinking</li></ul>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Notes">Notes</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Imre_Lakatos&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12" title="Edit section: Notes"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
