<li id="cite_note-19"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-19">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Lakatos, Worrall and Zahar (1976), <i>Proofs and Refutations</i> <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0-521-21078-X" title="Special:BookSources/0-521-21078-X">0-521-21078-X</a>, pp. 106–126, note that Poincaré's formal proof (1899) "Complèment à l'Analysis Situs", <i>Rediconti del Circolo Matematico di Palermo</i>, <b>13</b>, pp. 285–343, <a href="/wiki/Rewriting" title="Rewriting">rewrites</a> Euler's conjecture into a <a href="/wiki/Tautology_(logic)" title="Tautology (logic)">tautology</a> of <a href="/wiki/Vector_algebra" class="mw-disambig" title="Vector algebra">vector algebra</a><sup class="noprint Inline-Template" style="white-space:nowrap;">&#91;<i><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:WikiProject_Disambiguation/Fixing_links" title="Wikipedia:WikiProject Disambiguation/Fixing links"><span title="Link needs disambiguation (April 2024)">disambiguation needed</span></a></i>&#93;</sup>.</span>
